00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:58,695
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Is that where we're headed? -Yep.

43
00:03:59,197 --> 00:04:01,573
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The other side of the island is rock bluffs

44
00:04:01,658 --> 00:04:04,201
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}all the way down to the edge of the water.

