{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'd appreciate it if you'd hurry up about it.

48
00:04:14,587 --> 00:04:17,339
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Why? -Storm's coming.

49
00:04:43,741 --> 00:04:46,368
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Never seen a Marshals badge before.

50
00:04:48,037 --> 00:04:49,913
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm Deputy Warden McPherson, gentlemen.

51
00:04:49,998 --> 00:04:51,164
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Welcome to Shutter Island.

52
00:04:51,249 --> 00:04:54,293
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'll be the one taking you up to Ashecliffe.

53
00:05:06,597 --> 00:05:09,474
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Your boys seem a little on edge, Mr. McPherson.

54
00:05:09,559 --> 00:05:11,935
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Right now, Marshal, we all are.

55
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:58,231
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Electrified perimeter.

56
00:06:00,068 --> 00:06:01,818
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}How can you tell?

57
00:06:02,153 --> 00:06:04,738
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I've seen something like it before.

58
00:06:33,267 --> 00:06:37,187
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}All right. You gentlemen will be accorded all the help we can give,

59
00:06:37,271 --> 00:06:40,232
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}but during your stay, you will obey protocol.

60
00:06:40,316 --> 00:06:41,691
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Is that understood?

61
00:06:41,776 --> 00:06:43,151
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Absolutely.

62
00:06:43,611 --> 00:06:46,947
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The red brick building on your right is Ward A, the male ward.

63
00:06:47,031 --> 00:06:50,409
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Ward B, the female ward, is the one on your left.

64
00:06:50,493 --> 00:06:53,453
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Ward C is that building on the bluffs.

65
00:06:53,538 --> 00:06:55,122
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}An old Civil War fort.

66
00:06:55,206 --> 00:06:57,624
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The most dangerous patients are housed there.

67
00:06:57,708 --> 00:06:59,626
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Admittance to Ward C is forbidden

68
00:06:59,710 --> 00:07:02,379
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}without the written consent and physical presence

69
