{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}of both myself and Dr. Cawley.

70
00:07:05,091 --> 00:07:06,883
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Is that understood?

71
00:07:07,844 --> 00:07:10,262
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You act like insanity is catching.

72
00:07:13,141 --> 00:07:16,393
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You are hereby required to surrender your firearms.

73
00:07:17,895 --> 00:07:21,273
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Mr. McPherson, we are duly appointed federal marshals.

