00:07:21,357 --> 00:07:23,859
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We are required to carry our firearms with us at all times.

75
00:07:23,943 --> 00:07:26,945
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Executive order 31 9 of the Federal Code of Penitentiaries

76
00:07:27,029 --> 00:07:29,072
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}states that when inside a penitentiary,

77
00:07:29,157 --> 00:07:32,576
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}the officers of that institution have final authority.

78
00:07:35,455 --> 00:07:39,458
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Gentlemen, you will not get through this gate with your firearms.

79
00:07:58,895 --> 00:08:02,189
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Okay. Now that the official stuff's done, come on, boys,

