{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What do intelligence agencies want to consult a psychiatrist about?

99
00:09:32,863 --> 00:09:35,156
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I guess you'll have to ask him.

