101
00:09:45,001 --> 00:09:47,043
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Marshal Daniels. -Doctor.

102
00:09:47,503 --> 00:09:49,087
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Marshal Aule.

103
00:09:49,547 --> 00:09:52,257
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Thank you, Deputy Warden. That will be all.

104
00:09:52,341 --> 00:09:55,010
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Yes, sir. Pleasure, gentlemen.

105
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:58,346
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}He had a lot to say about you.

106
00:09:58,431 --> 00:10:01,641
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}McPherson's a good man. He believes in the work we do here.

107
00:10:01,726 --> 00:10:04,019
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And what would that be, exactly?

108
00:10:04,103 --> 00:10:07,772
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}疝 moral fusion between law and order and clinical care.

