{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}CHUCK: Pardon me, Doc. A what between what and what?

110
00:10:17,825 --> 00:10:20,869
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Those paintings are quite accurate.

111
00:10:20,953 --> 00:10:22,829
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Used to be the kind of patients we deal with here

112
00:10:22,913 --> 00:10:26,124
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}were shackled and left in their own filth.

113
00:10:26,208 --> 00:10:27,500
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They were beaten,

114
00:10:27,585 --> 00:10:29,836
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}as if whipping them bloody would drive the psychosis out.

115
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:32,005
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We drove screws into their brains,

116
00:10:32,089 --> 00:10:35,925
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}we submerged them in icy water until they lost consciousness

117
00:10:36,761 --> 00:10:38,470
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}or even drowned.

118
00:10:38,554 --> 00:10:40,513
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-And now? -We treat them.

119
00:10:40,598 --> 00:10:42,807
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Try to heal, try to cure.

120
00:10:42,892 --> 00:10:44,517
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And if that fails, at least we provide them

121
00:10:44,602 --> 00:10:47,854
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}with a measure of comfort in their lives. Calm.

122
00:10:47,938 --> 00:10:51,191
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}These are all violent offenders, right?

123
00:10:51,275 --> 00:10:53,526
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I mean, they've hurt people.

124
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:58,031
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Murdered them in some cases. -In almost all cases, yes.

125
00:10:58,115 --> 00:10:59,949
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Then, personally, Doctor, I'd have to say,

126
00:11:00,034 --> 00:11:02,410
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}screw their sense of calm.

127
00:11:03,996 --> 00:11:07,749
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It's my job to treat my patients, not their victims. I'm not here to judge.

128
00:11:07,833 --> 00:11:10,460
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-So this female prisoner... -Patient.

129
00:11:11,295 --> 00:11:13,213
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Excuse me. Patient,

130
