01:17:11,877 --> 01:17:14,003
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Did you ever find Laeddis?

1033
01:17:14,087 --> 01:17:16,005
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No. No, I never found him.

1034
01:17:16,089 --> 01:17:19,008
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Well, I got the next best thing. His intake form.

1035
01:17:19,092 --> 01:17:21,218
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It was the only thing in his files. There's no session notes,

1036
01:17:21,303 --> 01:17:25,014
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}no incident reports, no photographs, just this. It was weird.

1037
01:17:25,098 --> 01:17:26,766
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Here. Take a look.

1038
01:17:27,601 --> 01:17:28,934
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'll look at it later.

1039
01:17:30,937 --> 01:17:32,229
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What's the matter, boss?

1040
01:17:33,106 --> 01:17:35,608
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'll look it over later, that's all.

1041
01:17:37,569 --> 01:17:40,946
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Ashecliffe's that way. -I'm not going to Ashecliffe.

1042
01:17:42,449 --> 01:17:44,408
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm going to that lighthouse.

1043
01:17:44,493 --> 01:17:46,827
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm gonna find out what the fuck is happening on this island.

1044
01:18:00,967 --> 01:18:02,385
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}TEDDY: There it is.

1045
01:18:03,220 --> 01:18:07,223
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Damn. We're too far south. We're gonna have to double back.

1046
01:18:07,307 --> 01:18:09,517
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}There's no way we could cross those rocks.

1047
01:18:09,601 --> 01:18:11,268
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}There could be a way behind those trees.

1048
01:18:11,353 --> 01:18:14,438
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Maybe a path that goes around the rocks and leads over to the lighthouse.

1049
01:18:14,523 --> 01:18:15,564
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Boss... -Come on.

1050
01:18:15,649 --> 01:18:18,025
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Wait, wait, what are we doing? We got the intake form.

1051
01:18:18,110 --> 01:18:19,902
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It's proof there's a 67th patient,

1052
01:18:19,986 --> 01:18:22,822
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}which they said, repeatedly, doesn't exist.

1053
01:18:23,281 --> 01:18:26,492
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm getting to that lighthouse. You understand?

1054
01:18:28,829 --> 01:18:30,538
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What the hell can I say to you to stop you?

1055
01:18:30,622 --> 01:18:32,915
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Why would you want to, Chuck? Why?

1056
01:18:32,999 --> 01:18:34,834
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Because climbing down there when it's dark

1057
01:18:34,918 --> 01:18:38,087
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}is a thin step short of suicide, that's why.

1058
01:18:38,171 --> 01:18:41,590
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Okay, maybe you better sit this one out then.

1059
01:18:43,176 --> 01:18:45,177
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You brought me into this, boss,

1060
01:18:45,262 --> 01:18:48,597
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and now we're trapped here on this rock, on this island,

1061
01:18:48,682 --> 01:18:50,224
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}with no one to rely on but each other,

1062
01:18:50,308 --> 01:18:53,769
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-and now you're acting like... -Like what? Like what?

1063
01:18:54,396 --> 01:18:55,896
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}How am I acting?

1064
01:19:00,193 --> 01:19:03,654
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What the hell happened back there in those cells, Ted?

1065
01:19:08,368 --> 01:19:11,120
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What do you think the weather's like in Portland, Chuck?

1066
01:19:16,001 --> 01:19:17,251
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Seattle.

1067
01:19:20,464 --> 01:19:21,714
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm going on

1068
01:19:22,549 --> 01:19:23,758
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}alone.

1069
01:19:26,136 --> 01:19:29,013
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-I'm going with you, boss. -I said alone.

1070
01:19:30,724 --> 01:19:31,849
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Fine.

1071
01:19:58,502 --> 01:19:59,752
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Damn it!

1072
01:20:00,754 --> 01:20:02,046
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Damn it.

1073
01:20:07,260 --> 01:20:10,137
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I knew it wouldn't take long, but I couldn't get to it.

1074
01:20:10,222 --> 01:20:11,764
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The tide was up.

1075
01:20:20,023 --> 01:20:24,860
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Chuck!

1076
01:21:26,423 --> 01:21:27,673
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Come on!

1077
01:21:28,425 --> 01:21:29,800
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}(EXCLAIMS)

1078
01:22:03,043 --> 01:22:04,209
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Chuck!

1079
01:22:04,794 --> 01:22:06,712
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Where are you, Chuck?

1080
01:22:08,048 --> 01:22:09,423
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}(SQUEAKING)

1081
01:22:31,363 --> 01:22:35,449
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Chuck!

1082
01:23:16,324 --> 01:23:17,616
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}(GRUNTS)

1083
01:23:18,159 --> 01:23:19,868
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}(GASPING)

1084
01:23:19,953 --> 01:23:21,328
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Who are you?

1085
01:23:23,456 --> 01:23:26,291
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm Teddy Daniels. I'm a cop.

1086
01:23:27,669 --> 01:23:29,378
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You're the marshal.

1087
01:23:30,338 --> 01:23:32,006
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}That's right.

1088
01:23:34,175 --> 01:23:38,053
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Would you mind taking your hand from behind your back, please?

1089
01:23:38,138 --> 01:23:39,972
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Why? Why?

1090
01:23:41,474 --> 01:23:44,476
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I wanna make sure that what you're holding won't hurt me.

1091
01:23:52,152 --> 01:23:53,861
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm gonna keep this

1092
01:23:55,363 --> 01:23:56,864
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}if you don't mind.

1093
01:23:57,699 --> 01:23:59,116
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Fine by me.

1094
01:24:08,168 --> 01:24:09,501
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You're...

1095
01:24:10,920 --> 01:24:12,755
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You're Rachel Solando.

1096
01:24:14,340 --> 01:24:15,758
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The real one.

1097
01:24:19,763 --> 01:24:21,388
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Did you kill your children?

1098
01:24:23,183 --> 01:24:25,017
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I never had children.

1099
01:24:25,685 --> 01:24:27,478
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I was never married.

1100
01:24:29,022 --> 01:24:32,566
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And before I was a patient at Ashecliffe, I worked here.

1101
01:24:33,193 --> 01:24:35,778
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You... You were a nurse?

1102
01:24:38,114 --> 01:24:40,074
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I was a doctor, Marshal.

1103
01:24:43,495 --> 01:24:45,204
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You think I'm crazy.

1104
01:24:45,580 --> 01:24:48,916
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-No. No, no, I never... -And if I say I'm not crazy?

1105
01:24:50,126 --> 01:24:52,544
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Well, that hardly helps, does it?

1106
01:24:53,379 --> 01:24:55,881
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}That's the Kafkaesque genius of it.

1107
01:24:59,177 --> 01:25:01,470
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}People tell the world you're crazy,

1108
01:25:01,554 --> 01:25:05,474
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and all your protests to the contrary just confirm what they're saying.

1109
01:25:06,059 --> 01:25:09,228
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm not following you. I'm sorry.

1110
01:25:09,854 --> 01:25:11,814
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Once you're declared insane,

1111
01:25:11,898 --> 01:25:15,400
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}then anything you do is called part of that insanity.

1112
01:25:15,485 --> 01:25:21,073
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Reasonable protests are denial. Valid fears, paranoia.

1113
01:25:21,157 --> 01:25:22,741
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Survival instincts are

1114
01:25:23,743 --> 01:25:25,202
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}defense mechanisms.

1115
01:25:25,537 --> 01:25:29,248
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You're smarter than you look, Marshal. That's probably not a good thing.

1116
01:25:30,125 --> 01:25:32,793
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Tell me something. -Yeah.

1117
01:25:33,962 --> 01:25:35,754
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What happened to you?

1118
01:25:36,589 --> 01:25:40,008
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I started asking about these large shipments of sodium amytal

1119
01:25:40,093 --> 01:25:41,844
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and opium-based hallucinogens.

1120
01:25:41,928 --> 01:25:43,637
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Psychotropic drugs.

1121
01:25:45,014 --> 01:25:47,391
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I asked about the surgeries, too.

1122
01:25:49,435 --> 01:25:51,603
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You ever heard of a transorbital lobotomy?

1123
01:25:53,148 --> 01:25:55,858
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They zap the patient with electroshock,

1124
01:25:55,942 --> 01:25:58,777
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}then go through the eye with an ice pick,

1125
01:26:00,947 --> 01:26:03,031
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}pull out some nerve fibers.

1126
01:26:07,996 --> 01:26:09,329
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Tractable.

1127
01:26:10,790 --> 01:26:12,291
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It's barbaric,

1128
01:26:13,293 --> 01:26:14,793
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}unconscionable.

1129
01:26:15,795 --> 01:26:19,548
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Do you know how pain enters the body, Marshal? Do you?

1130
01:26:20,800 --> 01:26:22,259
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Depends on where you're hurt?

1131
01:26:22,343 --> 01:26:24,887
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No, it has nothing to do with the flesh.

1132
01:26:25,305 --> 01:26:27,306
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The brain controls pain.

1133
01:26:28,141 --> 01:26:32,519
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The brain controls fear, empathy, sleep, hunger, anger. Everything.

1134
01:26:34,856 --> 01:26:36,648
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What if you could control it?

1135
01:26:37,150 --> 01:26:40,152
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-You mean the brain? -Recreate a man

1136
01:26:40,820 --> 01:26:45,407
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}so he doesn't feel pain or love or sympathy.

1137
01:26:46,951 --> 01:26:48,410
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}A man who can't be interrogated,

1138
01:26:48,494 --> 01:26:51,205
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}because he has no memories to confess.

1139
01:26:53,791 --> 01:26:57,461
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You can never take away all a man's memories. Never.

1140
01:26:57,545 --> 01:27:01,673
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Marshal, the North Koreans used American POWs

1141
01:27:01,758 --> 01:27:03,425
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}during their brainwashing experiments.

1142
01:27:03,509 --> 01:27:06,929
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They turned soldiers into traitors. That's what they're doing here.

1143
01:27:07,013 --> 01:27:09,097
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They're creating ghosts to go out in the world

1144
01:27:09,182 --> 01:27:12,434
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and do things sane men... Sane men never would.

1145
01:27:12,518 --> 01:27:15,854
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}To have that kind of ability, that kind of knowledge,

1146
01:27:15,939 --> 01:27:18,607
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-that would take years. -Years. Years of research.

1147
01:27:18,691 --> 01:27:21,401
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Hundreds of patients to experiment on.

1148
01:27:22,654 --> 01:27:26,615
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Fifty years from now, people will look back and say, here, this place,

1149
01:27:26,950 --> 01:27:29,159
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}is where it all began.

1150
01:27:29,244 --> 01:27:34,039
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The Nazis used the Jews, Soviets used prisoners in their own Gulags, and we,

1151
01:27:34,874 --> 01:27:38,335
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}we tested patients on Shutter Island.

1152
01:27:40,004 --> 01:27:41,672
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No, they won't.

1153
01:27:42,632 --> 01:27:43,632
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No.

1154
01:27:46,094 --> 01:27:48,220
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You do understand

1155
01:27:50,765 --> 01:27:53,058
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}that they can't let you leave.

1156
01:27:53,351 --> 01:27:56,687
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I am a federal marshal. They can't stop me.

1157
01:27:58,064 --> 01:28:03,151
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I was an esteemed psychiatrist from a respected family.

1158
01:28:05,238 --> 01:28:06,863
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Didn't matter.

1159
01:28:09,575 --> 01:28:13,620
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Let me ask you. Any past traumas in your life?

1160
01:28:14,998 --> 01:28:16,248
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Yes.

1161
01:28:17,417 --> 01:28:19,501
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But why would that matter?

