{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}"Who wouldn't after what he'd been through?"

1167
01:28:34,267 --> 01:28:36,768
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They can say that about anyone, anyone at all.

1168
01:28:36,853 --> 01:28:39,813
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The point is they're gonna say it about you.

1169
01:28:43,067 --> 01:28:46,862
