{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No, I haven't.

1178
01:29:21,814 --> 01:29:24,566
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It takes 36 to 48 hours for neuroleptic narcotics

