01:29:24,650 --> 01:29:27,235
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}to reach workable levels in the bloodstream.

1180
01:29:29,030 --> 01:29:30,864
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Palsy comes first,

