01:30:46,023 --> 01:30:48,400
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm sorry, but you have to go.

1197
01:30:55,032 --> 01:30:56,658
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm gonna come back for you.

