01:31:09,213 --> 01:31:11,256
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You'll never leave here.

1203
01:31:20,600 --> 01:31:22,392
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I had a friend.

1204
01:31:22,477 --> 01:31:24,978
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I was with him yesterday, but we got separated.

1205
01:31:26,105 --> 01:31:27,772
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Have you seen him?

1206
01:31:28,941 --> 01:31:30,275
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Marshal,

1207
01:31:31,819 --> 01:31:33,945
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}you have no friends.

1208
01:31:38,117 --> 01:31:40,368
