1209
01:32:06,270 --> 01:32:07,812
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}There you are.

1210
01:32:10,650 --> 01:32:13,318
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We were wondering when you'd show up.

1211
01:32:14,946 --> 01:32:16,488
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Have a seat.

1212
01:32:16,948 --> 01:32:18,240
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Come on.

1213
01:32:28,918 --> 01:32:31,545
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Taking a leisurely stroll, were we?

1214
01:32:32,630 --> 01:32:35,674
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I was just looking around.

1215
01:32:38,636 --> 01:32:41,054
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Did you enjoy God's latest gift?

1216
01:32:42,682 --> 01:32:44,015
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-What? -God's gift.

1217
01:32:46,185 --> 01:32:47,519
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The violence.

1218
01:32:50,356 --> 01:32:54,734
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}When I came downstairs in my home and I saw that tree in my living room,

1219
01:32:54,819 --> 01:32:58,655
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}it reached out for me like a divine hand.

1220
01:33:00,866 --> 01:33:02,701
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}God loves violence.

