01:33:05,371 --> 01:33:08,206
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-I hadn't noticed. -(CHUCKLES) Sure you have.

1222
01:33:09,375 --> 01:33:11,543
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Why else would there be so much of it?

1223
01:33:11,877 --> 01:33:13,253
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It's in us.

1224
01:33:13,796 --> 01:33:15,130
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It's what we are.

1225
01:33:16,549 --> 01:33:18,883
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We wage war, we burn sacrifices,

1226
01:33:18,968 --> 01:33:21,511
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and pillage and plunder and tear at the flesh of our brothers.

