01:33:21,596 --> 01:33:25,515
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And why? Because God gave us violence to wage in his honor.

1228
01:33:28,728 --> 01:33:31,146
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I thought God gave us moral order.

1229
01:33:31,230 --> 01:33:34,232
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}There's no moral order as pure as this storm.

1230
01:33:39,030 --> 01:33:41,197
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}can my violence conquer yours?

1231
01:33:46,579 --> 01:33:48,997
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-I'm not violent. -Yes, you are.

1232
01:33:50,124 --> 01:33:52,542
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You're as violent as they come.

