01:33:53,252 --> 01:33:56,838
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I know this because I'm as violent as they come.

1234
01:33:56,922 --> 01:33:59,090
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}If the constraints of society were lifted,

1235
01:33:59,175 --> 01:34:01,843
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and I was all that stood between you and a meal,

1236
01:34:01,927 --> 01:34:05,305
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}you would crack my skull with a rock and eat my meaty parts.

1237
01:34:07,266 --> 01:34:08,850
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Wouldn't you?

1238
01:34:11,604 --> 01:34:14,064
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Cawley thinks you're harmless, that you can be controlled,

1239
01:34:14,148 --> 01:34:16,024
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}but I know different.

1240
01:34:16,651 --> 01:34:18,401
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-You don't know me. -Oh, but I do.

1241
01:34:18,486 --> 01:34:21,112
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-No, you don't. You don't know me at all. -Oh, I know you.

