01:34:21,739 --> 01:34:24,449
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We've known each other for centuries.

1243
01:34:33,793 --> 01:34:36,711
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}If I was to sink my teeth into your eye right now,

