01:34:44,261 --> 01:34:45,887
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Give it a try.

1246
01:34:47,431 --> 01:34:49,140
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}That's the spirit.

1247
01:35:23,884 --> 01:35:27,220
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Don't worry, because we're going to get you back to your room.

1248
01:35:28,139 --> 01:35:29,806
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Not really. -Something I've seen.

1249
01:35:29,890 --> 01:35:31,141
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Okay.

1250
01:35:36,355 --> 01:35:38,106
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Where have you been?

1251
01:35:38,190 --> 01:35:40,942
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Oh, just wandering. Just looking at your island.

