{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Stop looking at him. Stop looking at him.

1255
01:35:50,369 --> 01:35:52,203
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-Big meeting? -Oh, yes.

