{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}He subdued a highly dangerous patient quite handily.

1260
01:36:01,630 --> 01:36:02,630
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Is that so?

1261
