{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}George Noyce.

1263
01:36:06,552 --> 01:36:09,345
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}BRIDGET: Well, I don't remember what I'm supposed to remember.

1264
01:36:09,430 --> 01:36:11,139
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We're gated down. We're fine.

1265
01:36:11,223 --> 01:36:15,268
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}This Noyce, you said his name was, he's delusional?

1266
01:36:15,352 --> 01:36:18,062
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Oh, extremely. He can be quite upsetting.

1267
01:36:18,147 --> 01:36:19,856
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}As a matter of fact, two weeks ago,

