01:36:28,866 --> 01:36:30,658
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}No, thanks. I quit.

1271
01:36:31,744 --> 01:36:35,789
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}-So you're taking the ferry? -Yes, absolutely.

1272
01:36:35,873 --> 01:36:38,583
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I think we've gotten all we came here for, so...

