01:36:48,427 --> 01:36:50,136
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}My partner, Chuck.

1277
01:36:52,473 --> 01:36:55,308
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You don't have a partner, Marshal. You came here alone.

