{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Ever疝one wants a quick fix. They always have.

1281
01:37:05,444 --> 01:37:09,030
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I'm trying to do something that people, yourself included, don't understand.

1282
01:37:09,114 --> 01:37:12,075
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}And I'm not going to give up without a fight.

1283
01:37:13,911 --> 01:37:15,537
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I can see that.

1284
01:37:17,456 --> 01:37:18,581
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Mmm.

1285
01:37:19,625 --> 01:37:22,252
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}So, tell me again about your partner.

