01:37:23,963 --> 01:37:25,588
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What partner?

1287
01:37:25,965 --> 01:37:27,340
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}(LAUGHING)

